"{\"uid\": \"oann.com-newsroom-2-male-boxers-previously-barred-from-womens-events-will-fight-in-paris-olympics\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"OAN StaffJames Meyers11:33 AM - Wednesday, July 31, 2024 Two male boxers who were disqualified from competing with women at a global event last year have been allowed to fight in the Paris Olympics, the International Olympic Committee confirmed.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 246, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 3, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/One_America_News_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"OAN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/One_America_News_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/One_America_News_Network\"}, {\"begin\": 204, \"end\": 235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 32, \"to\": 41}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 43, \"to\": 47}, {\"ngram\": \"Two male boxers\", \"from\": 57, \"to\": 72}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 115, \"to\": 120}, {\"ngram\": \"a global event\", \"from\": 124, \"to\": 138}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 179, \"to\": 197}]}, {\"sentence\": \"two trans athletes allowed to compete in Olympics BOXING \\ud83e\\udd4athe international olympics committee has cleared two trans athletes ( Imane Khalif and Lin Yu-Ting) to compete in boxing despite failing the required gender tests put in place by the boxing federation.\", \"from\": 248, \"to\": 507, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 394, \"end\": 405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lin Yu-Ting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two trans athletes\", \"from\": 248, \"to\": 266}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics BOXING\", \"from\": 289, \"to\": 304}, {\"ngram\": \"the international olympics committee\", \"from\": 306, \"to\": 342}, {\"ngram\": \"two trans athletes\", \"from\": 355, \"to\": 373}, {\"ngram\": \"Imane Khalif\", \"from\": 376, \"to\": 388}, {\"ngram\": \"boxing\", \"from\": 420, \"to\": 426}, {\"ngram\": \"the required gender tests\", \"from\": 443, \"to\": 468}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 476, \"to\": 481}, {\"ngram\": \"the boxing federation\", \"from\": 485, \"to\": 506}]}, {\"sentence\": \"the move has\\u2026pic.twitter.com/vacDZ0Bumv Imane Khelif of Algeria and Lin Yu\\u2011ting of Taiwan failed to meet gender eligibility tests at the Women's World Boxing Championships in New Delhi last year, causing the males to be disqualified.\", \"from\": 508, \"to\": 742, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 550, \"end\": 562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421623295, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 566, \"end\": 573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.999999520532698, \"rank\": 4.3900323499359085e-07, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 593, \"end\": 599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"score\": 0.9966728692341246, \"rank\": 0.003259549331676506, \"text\": \"Taiwan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\"}, {\"begin\": 661, \"end\": 667, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\", \"score\": 0.999999999438387, \"rank\": 5.580691446029528e-10, \"text\": \"Boxing\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\"}, {\"begin\": 685, \"end\": 694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\", \"score\": 0.9998378587438543, \"rank\": 0.00016114151879844605, \"text\": \"New Delhi\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the move\", \"from\": 508, \"to\": 516}, {\"ngram\": \"Lin Yu\\u2011ting\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 587}, {\"ngram\": \"gender eligibility tests\", \"from\": 613, \"to\": 637}, {\"ngram\": \"the males\", \"from\": 712, \"to\": 721}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the time of their disqualifications, the president of the International Boxing Association (IBA), which governs the World Boxing Championships, alleged that the boxers' chromosome tests came back as XY (women typically have two X chromosomes, while men typically have an X and a Y chromosome).\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 1040, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 806, \"end\": 838, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8510269401268503e-17, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 840, \"end\": 843, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9973494857314037, \"rank\": 0.0024066002249330453, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 947, \"end\": 949, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"score\": 0.777088121899103, \"rank\": 0.2868553045107047, \"text\": \"XY\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 755}, {\"ngram\": \"their disqualifications\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 782}, {\"ngram\": \"the president\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 797}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Boxing Championships\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 889}, {\"ngram\": \"the boxers' chromosome tests\", \"from\": 904, \"to\": 932}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 955}, {\"ngram\": \"two X chromosomes\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 988}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 999}, {\"ngram\": \"an X\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1019}, {\"ngram\": \"a Y chromosome\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1038}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Based on DNA tests, we identified a number of athletes who tried to trick their colleagues into posing as women,\\\" the association's president, Umar Kremlev, told Russia's Tass news agency at the time.\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1243, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1187, \"end\": 1191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Umar\", \"score\": 0.9999996524227903, \"rank\": 3.425748717128647e-07, \"text\": \"Umar\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Umar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Umar\"}, {\"begin\": 1206, \"end\": 1212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9998885756185167, \"rank\": 9.184594604300642e-05, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 1215, \"end\": 1231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TASS\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tass news agency\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TASS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TASS\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"DNA tests\", \"from\": 1052, \"to\": 1061}, {\"ngram\": \"a number\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1085}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1097}, {\"ngram\": \"their colleagues\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1133}, {\"ngram\": \"posing\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1145}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1154}, {\"ngram\": \"the association's president\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1184}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 1234, \"to\": 1242}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"According to the results of the tests, it was proved that they have XY chromosomes.\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1328, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the results\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1269}, {\"ngram\": \"the tests\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1282}, {\"ngram\": \"XY chromosomes\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1327}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Such athletes were excluded from competition.\\\"\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1375, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Such athletes\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1342}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1373}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the two have been cleared to compete in the women's 66-kilogram and women's 57-kilogram matches in Paris this week, the IOC confirmed in an email Tuesday.\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1540, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1486, \"end\": 1491, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999995672431877, \"rank\": 4.327570136513661e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1507, \"end\": 1510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1254594793265426e-23, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the women's 66-kilogram\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1449}, {\"ngram\": \"women's 57-kilogram matches\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1481}, {\"ngram\": \"an email\", \"from\": 1523, \"to\": 1531}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ruling received backlash from female boxer and Australian captain Caitlin Parker, who said this could be very dangerous for the sport.\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1680, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1594, \"end\": 1604, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.993964728433759, \"rank\": 0.005295476300268387, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 1613, \"end\": 1627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Parker\", \"score\": 0.9999997772802337, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caitlin Parker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Parker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Parker\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The ruling\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1552}, {\"ngram\": \"backlash\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1570}, {\"ngram\": \"female boxer\", \"from\": 1576, \"to\": 1588}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1670, \"to\": 1679}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not agree with them being allowed to compete in sport, especially combat sports,\\\" Parker said.\", \"from\": 1682, \"to\": 1782, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1771, \"end\": 1777, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aloysius_Parker\", \"score\": 0.946543482908063, \"rank\": 0.05647524133644409, \"text\": \"Parker\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aloysius_Parker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aloysius_Parker\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1736, \"to\": 1741}, {\"ngram\": \"especially combat sports\", \"from\": 1743, \"to\": 1767}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It can be incredibly dangerous.\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1816, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not agree with it,\\\" she continued.\", \"from\": 1817, \"to\": 1856, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not like I have not sparred men before.\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 1902, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 1891, \"to\": 1894}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But you know it can be dangerous for combat sports and it should be seriously looked into.\\\"\", \"from\": 1903, \"to\": 1994, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"combat sports\", \"from\": 1940, \"to\": 1953}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Yes, biologically \\u2026 genetically they are going to have more advantages and in combat sports it can be dangerous,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2120, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more advantages\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2067}, {\"ngram\": \"combat sports\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2088}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I really hope the organizations get their act together so that boxing can continue to be at the Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2228, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the organizations\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2153}, {\"ngram\": \"their act\", \"from\": 2158, \"to\": 2167}, {\"ngram\": \"boxing\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2191}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2214, \"to\": 2226}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Women's boxing was only introduced in 2012 and I want to see it for the next 100, 200 years to come,\\\" she concluded.\", \"from\": 2230, \"to\": 2347, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Women's boxing\", \"from\": 2231, \"to\": 2245}, {\"ngram\": \"200 years\", \"from\": 2313, \"to\": 2322}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Khelif is slated to compete against Italy's Angela Carinin on Thursday, and Lin is set to fight against Uzbekistan's Sitora Turdibekova on Friday.\", \"from\": 2349, \"to\": 2506, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2397, \"end\": 2402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.8012928517699444, \"rank\": 0.1607998419017676, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}, {\"begin\": 2465, \"end\": 2475, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uzbekistan\", \"score\": 0.9999999916994966, \"rank\": 5.461375344939538e-09, \"text\": \"Uzbekistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uzbekistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uzbekistan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 2360, \"to\": 2366}, {\"ngram\": \"Thursday\", \"from\": 2422, \"to\": 2430}, {\"ngram\": \"Lin\", \"from\": 2436, \"to\": 2439}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2505}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stay informed!\", \"from\": 2508, \"to\": 2522, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Receive breaking news blasts directly to your inbox for free.\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2584, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"breaking news blasts\", \"from\": 2531, \"to\": 2551}, {\"ngram\": \"your inbox\", \"from\": 2564, \"to\": 2574}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Subscribe here.https://www.oann.com/alerts What do YOU think?\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2649, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Click here to jump to the comments!\", \"from\": 2650, \"to\": 2685, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the comments\", \"from\": 2672, \"to\": 2684}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Share this post!\", \"from\": 2689, \"to\": 2705, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\"